# Jvkrog — Autonomous Systems & Decision Engineering

> Building systems that observe, decide, and act — with minimal human dependency.

---

##  Featured Projects

###  TAlgo-X — Multi-Engine Trading System
Production-grade trading execution system with dual-engine architecture and real-time decision logic.

- Multi-engine design (FAST + SLOW execution layers)
- ALMA-based adaptive strategy (fast + slow)
- Position persistence using SQLite
- Lifecycle control (session handling, EOD risk management)
- Real-time alerts via Telegram

---

###  TAlgo — Adaptive Trading Engine
Rule-based, real-time trading system designed to eliminate emotional decision-making.

- Event-driven architecture (WebSocket + OHLC pipeline)
- Indicator-based strategy (EMA, HMA, ALMA)
- State-machine decision system
- Fully explainable via logs

 Docs:  
- [Architecture](https://github.com/Jvkrog/TAlgo/blob/main/Docs/architecture.md)  
- [Strategy](https://github.com/Jvkrog/TAlgo/blob/main/Docs/strategy.md)

---

###  WiFi Car (ESP32-CAM Rover)
Real-time video streaming rover with web-based control.

- ESP32-CAM streaming  
- Remote navigation via browser  
- Embedded motor control (L298N)  

---

###  FireBot
Mobile fire detection system with IoT monitoring.

- Sensor-based fire detection  
- Real-time alerts  
- Remote monitoring capability  

